La madoda amabili abevele eNkantolo yeMantshi eMzimkhulu, izolo ngecala lokubulala uMnuz Ndumiso Jali (72) nomkakhe uNkk Noma-India Jali (70) abadutshulwa babulawa besemzini wabo ngoJanuwari. Kulesi sigameko kwathathwa imali elinganiselwa kuR170 000 eyayisendlini. UJali obengumfundisi weCrusade Church kuthiwa wake wasebenzisana noMnuz Siphiwo Mancoba ongumsunguli webandla iSeven Angels Church,  eseNgcobo, e-Eastern 
Cape. Ngesikhathi besebenzisana amalungu ebandla labo ayekhonzela etendeni elaligxunyekwe emzini kaJali. Abasolwa bayingxenye yabayisithupha abasolwa ngokubulala amaphoyisa asesiteshini saseNgcobo. Batshele inkantolo ukuthi abamdingi ummeli bazozikhulumela. Bavele imizuzwana enkantolo, icala labo lahlehliselwa uLwesibili oluzayo. Ngalolu suku kulindeleke ukuthi bacele ibheyili.